snippet.textDisplay:
To Coca Cola Management sponsoring Coke Studios in so many countries of the world producing creative and entertaining musical creations that attract people of the world regardless of their mother tongue:Pakistan Coke Studio may be the best of them. I was In Canada in 1969 when the Woodstock Music Festival was held in the US. It was the unique and most famous festival
for the world wide creative artists. I think it is about time to have a similar and even better and greater COKE STUDIO
MUSIC FESTIVAL to be set up somewhere in California, USA and invite all the countries participating in Coke Studio musical creations to come to the festival. This would be the greatest musical festival ever and will be attended and watched by almost all the world population. I sincerely request the Coke Studio to look into setting up such a healthy, peaceful and extremely entertaining festival to bring the world together.
